      <title>韩国的婚姻状况结束了长达十年之久的下降趋势，这对生育造成了影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/south-korea-s-marriages-end-decade-long-decline-that-hurt-births</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，韩国的结婚率出现了大约十年来的首次上升，这是该国全球生育率最低的一个因素出现了罕见的改善迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/south-korea-s-marriages-end-decade-long-decline-that-hurt-births</guid>
